rComments: This is the worst prof I have had in my 4 years at the University of Ottawa. He is difficult to understand and then penalizes people for not participating in discussion - but how can you participate if you can't understand a single thing he says? Very unhelpful and hardly available. Do not take this class if you don't have to.

Seriously horrible. I've never had so much trouble understanding a prof (his accent) but also how he structures his classes. SO unorganized. and his grading is ridiculous. worst exam! It doesn't reflect anything in the class. I am a law student and I had trouble in this undergraduate class. tells you a lot
He makes the most random diagrams and is a pretty boring lecturer. But he's a fair prof and not a bad teacher.
Says a lot in class, without really saying anything.  Mandatory readings can be found online, 99% of the time.
